author: tellison
msg: Partial fix for HARMONY-5077 ([classlib][io] a stress test org.apache.harmony.test.stress.api.java.io.stress.readers.StringReader.StringReaderWriterStressTest.testManyStreams deadlocks).
Testing shows that the string in a StringReader is not considered the lock object, and the lock object is not used in close().
